    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH7x2028-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:10:27.969+09:00">and indeed you are."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:56:51.58+09:00">"The fire is burning thy                        lower garments."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:16:20.068+09:00">Then the other gathered his garment, and                        the fire expired.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:19:03.768+09:00">Greatly incensed, he said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:01:59.241+09:00">"You have been noticing it for a long                        time,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:21:12.152+09:00">why did you not mention it                        earlier?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:30:28.96+09:00">Quoth our man:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:11:21.866+09:00">One winter day someone with a phlegmatic temper was standing                        around a fireplace together with others.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:00:44.304+09:00">He noticed that the tailend of                        somebody else's lower garment had caught fire,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:48:26.817+09:00">and so he said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2019-12-19T21:21:39.535+09:00">"There is a certain matter</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:48:51.78+09:00">that I noticed quite some                        time ago,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:33:20.914+09:00">and I wished to bring it                        up</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:24:32.475+09:00">but I feared that thou wert                        hot-headed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:24:45.221+09:00">If I do not bring it up,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:56:02.209+09:00">I fear that thou shall be hurt too severely.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:52:25.704+09:00">Now then, would it be right to bring it up?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:52:43.058+09:00">Or would it be right not to bring it up?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:54:23.356+09:00">The other asked what the                        matter was.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:30:13.107+09:00">Quoth the man:</seg>
                <seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T04:47:17.91+09:00"/><seg corresp="#CH7x2028_CHANT_049-46a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2022-11-16T05:03:08.761+09:00">"I said thou art hot-headed,</seg></p>
            </div>
